# Claude Code internal state · everything under .claude/ EXCEPT path-scoped rules.
# Path-scoped agent rules ARE committed (planning-003 §A.4.2 · AlphaDawg pattern).
# Pattern: ignore .claude/* (file or dir directly under .claude/), then re-include the rules subdir.
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
CLAUDE.md.local

# Internal asset-generation tooling (X/Twitter card images for launch
