# `build/` (above) is intentionally ignored at any depth as build-output dirs.
# Exception: docs/build/ holds the build-progress + engineering log narratives
# (BUILD_PROGRESS.md, ENGINEERING_DEBUG_LOG.md, TEST_REPORT.md, BUILD.md).
# Those files ARE tracked — without this re-include, edits to them silently
# don't stage. (Found in cron-sweep 2026-05-10 when canonicalizing the
# deployments path across operator runbooks.)
!docs/build/
!docs/build/**

