# Visual evidence — kept locally, organized by round / surface; not pushed.
# Exception: screenshots/readme/ holds the 6 README "Visual tour" PNGs
# committed for GitHub render (planning-003 §A.2.2). Refresh via
# `pnpm screenshots:refresh` against a live Studio dev server.
# (Use `screenshots/*` not `screenshots/` so the unignore on the
# subdirectory below actually takes effect — git won't traverse into a
# fully-ignored parent dir.)
screenshots/*
!screenshots/readme/

# MetaMask Playwright profile dirs (runtime artefacts, not code)
scripts/qa/metamask-e2e/mm/

# Python cache from scripts/verifier-py/
scripts/verifier-py/__pycache__/

# Test target scratch files (operator's local docs / receipts / etc.)
test-targets/*
# Exception: dd-batch/ holds the 3 vendor-agreement fixtures for the
# `ivaronix doc bulk` flow (planning-01 §4B · DD-analyst batch audit).
# Tracked, not ignored. The pre-sweep-85 gitignore was a single
# `test-targets/` line that contradicted git ls-files (which had the
# 3 dd-batch/ fixtures tracked anyway).
!test-targets/dd-batch/
!test-targets/dd-batch/**

# _archive/ holds pre-v2 planning docs (kept for history; do not edit).
# Tracked, not ignored — the README docs grid + planning-003 §A.5.X
# both reference these files. Earlier `_archive/` entry in this file
# was self-contradicting drift; removed.

.vercel
cowork-opinion.md

